Pantron heard the order and quickly got on the comm. He had the computer scan for all possible hailing frequencies. The computer narrowed it down to  two frequencies. He had the comp run  both hopefully the one wrong frequency wont be heard by an unfriendly foe. 

  cyberwolf4@... wrote: 
Phobia continues to scan the space around Earth, he spotted yet 
another ship aproaching at high speed, "full magnification" Phobia 
called out." What's this?" 

Full magnification showed predicon markings. "That's all I need." If 
the predicons tracked him down all the way from cybertron he'd be up 
on charges of desertion. But only if they learn that he wasn't 
deleated by the temporal storm.

He knew that sooner or later he'd have to face the predicons. He 
hoped it would be on his terms, and as an ally, not defending his 
actions as a deserter.

"Pantron I think you may be able to help me after all. Get on the 
comm, see if you can raise that ship."

THe new ship was travelling an erratic path, and to fast to be ynder 
control. Phobia hoped, for his own sake,  that it would crash without 
survivors.
